videos.headline: Rogers on MS State Air Raid: 'We can be explosive'
videos.description: After throwing for 415 yards and six touchdowns to lead Mississippi State's 43-34 comeback win over Auburn, QB Will Rogers states the obvious.

videos.headline: Mississippi State roars back to stun No. 17 Auburn
videos.description: The Bulldogs rally from a 28-point deficit for the largest comeback victory in school history and then hold off the Tigers, 43-34.
